7%2F11%2F06%2F175051_dca39e78f67507fdac02d7455f4f5d34.jpg&h=d887bfb0&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n⭐&lt;- 呢個係花形? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嚴格黎講星星係遠距離嘅星體，唔會係⭐️嘅形狀<br />\n你又知⭐️唔係花形？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n繼續駁啦撚樣🌺🌸🌼🌻🌹🌷💐</blockquote><br />\n你堆符號第二個都係咁嘅形狀喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89ac5aa1d4a98a7fb5fffe8cc82111f73ad22a42","tid":459991,"uid":53632,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T10:50:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>上面成班傻閪笑乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔可以係花形？<br />\n人笑你又笑<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/06/175051_dca39e78f67507fdac02d7455f4f5d34.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F06%2F175051_dca39e78f67507fdac02d7455f4f5d34.jpg&h=d887bfb0&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n⭐&lt;- 呢個係花形? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嚴格黎講星星係遠距離嘅星體，唔會係⭐️嘅形狀<br />\n你又知⭐️唔係花形？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n嚴格黎講星星係恆星，係球形嘅<br />\n而花形呢，三角形係花形，正方形係花形，五邊形係花形，圓形都係花形，ok u win<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/06/184405_7d7ec0c48e5a4193b14fab8446090c58.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F06%2F184405_7d7ec0c48e5a4193b14fab8446090c58.jpg&h=11522df8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n知唔知乜野叫common sense <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af7a836767f9113151e360a4cb7032bbb824d328","tid":459991,"uid":155067,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy"