29d15e073d","tid":459991,"uid":46231,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T11:08:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>上面成班傻閪笑乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔可以係花形？<br />\n人笑你又笑<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/06/175051_dca39e78f67507fdac02d7455f4f5d34.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F06%2F175051_dca39e78f67507fdac02d7455f4f5d34.jpg&h=d887bfb0&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n⭐&lt;- 呢個係花形? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嚴格黎講星星係遠距離嘅星體，唔會係⭐️嘅形狀<br />\n你又知⭐️唔係花形？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n嚴格黎講星星係恆星，係球形嘅<br />\n而花形呢，三角形係花形，正方形係花形，五邊形係花形，圓形都係花形，ok u win<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/06/184405_7d7ec0c48e5a4193b14fab8446090c58.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F06%2F184405_7d7ec0c48e5a4193b14fab8446090c58.jpg&h=11522df8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n知唔知乜野叫common sense <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你要講晒咁多真實例子做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n的確係成個天咁多星體 無一個係你所謂嘅星形<br />\n而又的確有花係咁嘅形狀 你舉再多唔係咁形狀嘅花都改變唔到事實架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有關乜野common sense事  形狀同事物嘅聯想人人唔同 一定要係星先叫有common sense咩?<br />\n<br />\n連埋個女仔個頭  中個有個圓形咁 我都覺得似花多d喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a542f327772877d2f11d4521dd241fbe78dbc71","tid":459991,"uid":46231,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T11:12:18.000Z","msg":"開口埋口有冇common sense果位<br />\n我想問下咁樣係似星定似花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/06/191216_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F06%2F191216_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=515f0d00&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1e3c7fba10a148fc9a9c7f5a2d6aa082d42b3bed","tid":459991,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T11:14:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c91d02c3fe8e1353d494fae5c30d5ca6f200d5fc","tid":459991,"uid":623,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T11:14:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/06/191429_572064f8627a6d5a5240ad7a77d792cb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F06%2F191429_572064f8627a6d5a5240ad7a77d792cb.jpg&h=9be54e90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n都唔夠梁家輝呢個經典造型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a3913f56bdd227e19fb84260a44e8a48dcdca75","tid":459991,"uid":132896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T11:37:48.000Z","msg":"有咩好嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5c0a4e12ab87f7ff750ef147f49095044b1d23f","tid":459991,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T11:38:52.000Z","msg":"唔知"},{"pid":"26b0e7e72560f8d950cefc6b14fcd53105beb6fc","tid":459991,"uid":114692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T11:41:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":